data.description: Discover your next home in Champions Park with this immaculate 2-story beauty! This residence boasts an open floor plan, freshly painted, and is adorned with high ceilings. Step into expansive living room, complete with a cleverly integrated office cove. The heart of the home, the open island kitchen, includes stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, and breakfast bar. Adjacent to the kitchen the breakfast nook invites you to start your day on a bright note. The first floor also includes a formal dining room and home office space. The second floor boasts a spacious loft, perfect as a family room or game room for all ages. The primary suite is a sanctuary of sophistication, featuring a sitting room that adds a touch of luxury to your daily routine. The ensuite bath is a vision of modern comfort, enhanced by California closets. Two secondary bedrooms complete this level, offering versatility and space for all. Eco-conscious living is seamlessly integrated into this home's design, with energy-efficient features including a tankless water heater, energy star appliances, a high-efficiency water heater, and storm windows and doors that protect and insulate. Outside, the backyard features a covered patio boasting retractable privacy screens. Even the garage is ingeniously equipped with a retractable privacy screen, maximizing both function and aesthetics. Champions Park is conveniently located near shopping destinations, renowned golf courses, La Cantera Mall, the Hyatt Hill Country Resort, and the University of Texas at San Antonio. Don't miss your chance to make this extraordinary residence yours, book your personal tour today!
